{"tid":1122545,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"台灣中天新聞不演了！ 將台灣直接納入畫滿五星紅旗的中國版圖","createTime":"2019-04-24T04:10:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-24T06:32:45.000Z","uid":35790,"like":37,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"49bb91221f6abf192383a5645855b275fcef0a4c","tid":1122545,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-24T04:10:33.000Z","msg":"中天新聞不演了！ 台灣直接納入中國版圖<br />\n<br />\n發布 2019.04.24 <br />\n<img src=\"https://s.newtalk.tw/album/news/238/5cbfbd9f060a4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.newtalk.tw%2Falbum%2Fnews%2F238%2F5cbfbd9f060a4.jpg&h=ce989014&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n中天新聞被視為親中色彩相當濃厚的媒體，但在昨天新聞台的報導中，引用一張中國地圖，其中居然直接納入「台灣」。   圖：翻攝自臉書粉專《打馬悍將粉絲團》<br />\n<br />\n中天新聞被視為親中色彩濃厚的媒體，但昨（23）天新聞台的報導中，引用一張中國地圖，其中居然直接納入「台灣」，彷彿意指台灣是中國的一部分。畫面流傳到網路上，也立刻受到眾多網友的大力撻伐，直呼應該要再重罰。<br />\n<br />\n這張將台灣納入了畫滿五星紅旗的中國地圖，其實是去（107）年5月中天新聞「看見新中國」的節目中，出現在畫面中的螢幕背板。後來遭民眾向NCC檢舉不符政治現況，中天有預設政治立場。NCC也在同年9月發函請中天召開內部自律與倫理委員會討論，並要求將會議記錄公開供外界檢視。NCC當時也表示會將此案做為未來中天評鑑及換照參考。<br />\n<br />\n中天新聞以立場親中、用詞浮誇偏頗聞名，今（108）年上（3）月更因部分新聞內容未經查證等，受到國家通訊傳播委員會（NCC）裁罰100萬元。本月更因為盜用公視影劇《我們與惡的距離》的部分畫面做為新聞畫面，受到各界批評。<br />\n<br />\n臉書粉專《打馬悍將粉絲團》昨晚PO文指出，「中天把台灣列為中華人民共和國的一部分」，隨文附的圖是一張將台灣納入了畫滿五星紅旗的中國地圖。粉專痛批「這種媒體，竟還可以在台灣生存...」<br />\n<a href=\"https://newtalk.tw/news/view/2019-04-24/237398?fbclid=IwAR2glbTDhH75HDVzO0d7cmqLJ1sqW0wHGE7kKw7q-r70zyNY5f6TGLbHtAo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnewtalk.tw%2Fnews%2Fview%2F2019-04-24%2F237398%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR2glbTDhH75HDVzO0d7cmqLJ1sqW0wHGE7kKw7q-r70zyNY5f6TGLbHtAo&d=zdm3SfM4sEUVnXmiquxubL7zmW0KSjJ%2FkJHMgTQKA%2BU%3D&h=8a0e2e78\" target=\"_blank\">https://newtalk.tw/news/view/2019-04-24/237398?fbclid=IwAR2glbTDhH75HDVzO0d7cmqLJ1sqW0wHGE7kKw7q-r70zyNY5f6TGLbHtAo</a>"},{"pid":"7ea23a59e8dbfea168f1a9f7ddc5b89906932114","tid":1122545,"uid":20867,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-24T04:13:43.000Z","msg":"Treason"},{"pid":"1fe131f1f6d961954afcc14c62b1e5836cc2a3ac","tid":1122545,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-24T04:17:14.000Z","msg":"中天電視股份有限公司（簡稱中天；英語：CTI Television Inc.）是中華民國的一家衛星電視台，隸屬於旺中集團，旗下有中天新聞台、中天綜合台、中天娛樂台三個台灣境內頻道及中天亞洲台、中天北美台兩個境外頻道。<br />\n<a href=\"https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/zh-tw/中天電視\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.m.wikipedia.org%2Fzh-tw%2F%E4%B8%AD%E5%A4%A9%E9%9B%BB%E8%A6%96&d=zdm3SfM4sEUVnXmiquxubL7zmW0KSjJ%2FkJHMgTQKA%2BU%3D&h=50e7cff6\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/zh-tw/中天電視</a><br />\n仲有中時 旺旺"},{"pid":"abbfe003f882a287f12f828d3db36f56d5befbec","tid":1122545,"uid":123456,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-24T04:18:18.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">中天發大財</span>"},{"pid":"cd2ed83d2f06472e369f56f21974012941e9d5c8","tid":1122545,"uid":197337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-24T04:18:35.000Z","msg":"反了反了"},{"pid":"d18d48631a26b1a91479fd1a869a62d90ae23163","tid":1122545,"uid":48234,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-24T04:20:00.000Z","msg":"共諜喎<br />\n死刑啦"},{"pid":"adc0392d83465db0f722f2959bd7e8bad8f3f753","tid":1122545,"uid":57376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-24T04:36:51.000Z","msg":"要發財，不了"},{"pid":"7dc09411a7e36c8d8fae37efa199900522d2470f","tid":1122545,"uid":28195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-24T04:39:19.000Z","msg":"中天在台灣，係咪即係當年香港亞視？"},{"pid":"4fa0c59a347782775ac348146872c529d6553928","tid":1122545,"uid":63909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-24T04:39:29.000Z","msg":"台灣喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4322deb96e22a7fc3abcef426f3501733a7b9662","tid":1122545,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"adc0392d83465db0f722f2959bd7e8bad8f3f753","tid":1122545,"uid":57376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-24T04:36:51.000Z","msg":"要發財，不了"},"citedB